name: Nail Polish with Detail Pen
description: These are really cool!! The Nail Candy polish pens are not only modern but distinctive in its potential.  Each pen consists of two different colors, each with its own brush and micro-tip detail pen.  The pen lets users be able to really create art on the small canvases of their nails.  By gently squeezing the bottle while either drawing or dragging the pen, this allows you to create any type of design you desire.  Custard has a great instructional video on our webpage!  Get these while they last! Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Anklet Socks
description: These cute socks come from Sweet Marcel, a new addition to the Custard line family!  These socks are super comfortable and very affordable.  They are handmade in Turkey and are all one size.  Custard has three different prints in the anklet socks (see images), all of which will add great color and excitement to your outfit!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Knee-High Socks
description: These wonderful socks are made in the USA by Sweet Marcel.  Custard has plenty of cool pattern designs available in the knee-highs and they are so comfortable!  We have four styles of these knee-high socks that are actually made from recycled yarn which we love here at Custard!  These socks come just below the knee and are great to wear with all types shoes and boots. Don't miss your chance to get a pair of these hot new items from Custard! Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Love Studs
description: Let this studs say the thing that is on your mind!  The love studs are oxidized brass and are handmade in Portland, OR!  Each earring is 1 inch in diameter.  This item is very affordable and easy to pair with most outfits!

name: Tiny Deer Necklace
description: Even though the pendant on this item is tiny it can still pack a punch!  The piece is handmade in Austin, TX and is all brass.  The chain is 16 inches and the deer is approximately .33 inches wide and .5 inch tall.  This piece is excellent layered with other necklaces and is just plain fun!   Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Over-the-Knee Socks
description: These socks are perfect for the fall and winter months!  These socks are from Sweet Marcel and are handmade in Turkey.  They are all one size and this style in particular will rise just above the knee, giving you not warmth and comfort but a great look!  Custard has three different styles of the over-the-knee socks for you to choose from.  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Loyal Friend Necklace
description: This fun little piece is handmade in Austin, TX and is all brass! The fox pendant is approximately a .25 inch wide and .5 inch tall.  The hands and heart charm is approximately .75 inches wide and a .25 inch tall.  The chain is 16 inches.  Tracking and insurance is included in shipping price.

name: Heart Padlock Necklace
description: A perfect gift for that special loved one!  This piece is simple yet very symbolic!  The necklace has a 17 inch aged brass chain.  The heart padlock pendant is 3/8 of an inch across and is also aged brass.  The necklace is handmade in Austin, TX!  Tracking and shipping are included in the shipping price.

name: ADA Leather Hook Bracelet
description:
Hip, fun and stylish you will just love this ADA hook bracelet. They are perfect for any occasion. They come in many awesome colours to pair with an everyday look as well as adding something special to an evening inspired ensemble. The ADA Hook Bracelet is pretty, and delicate with gold hook detailing. It layers well with other Hook Bracelets, as well as bangles and watches.  Add one to your wrist or load up with the layered look.  As always, if you need more than what is listed in stock, please call us, and these bracelets fit almost everyone, so they make great gifts.  Made in the USA! 
In the group photo, from left to right: Red, Pink, Purple, Brown, Mustard, Tan, Silver, Blue, Black

name: State Pride Necklace
description: Be sure to grab these darling little necklaces to show support for your state!!  These pieces are handmade in Half Moon Bay, CA by Kris Nations.  Each pendant is cut from recycled sheets of metal and have a 14 karat gold overlay.  The state pendants measure at approximately 1 square inch and the chain is 18 inches long.  The packaging with these necklaces is also incredible!  They come in little, corked glass bottles..so cute!  Make sure you grab yours fast! Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Helmet Mask Necklace
description: Remember Nacho Libre??  That's what I think of when I see this piece from Monserat De Lucca.  It's made of brass and is really quite cool.  The lucha libra mask pendant is approximately 1.25 inches tall and 1 inch at it's widest point.  The chain is measures in at 14 inches and is a great layering piece.  Don't forget the back of the mask pendant too which has a really cool laces detail!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Letter Necklace
description: These necklaces make the perfect simple gifts for anyone!! They are from Lotus Jewelry Studio and made in Baltimore.  The letter pendants measure at .5 inch by .5 inch.  They are made of 14-karat gold fill.  Custard has available the letters S, T, M, C, & E.  The chain measures in at 16 inches and is a beaded curb chain.  These pieces are really affordable and are really easy to style with other necklaces as well! Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Revolver Necklace
description: This piece is a favorite amongst Custard employees!! It's a 100% brass revolver necklace from Monserat de Lucca.  The revolver pendant is 1.5 inches tall at its highest point and 2.5 inches across.  The chamber actually rotates and the gun just shines!  The chain is approximately 14.5 inches long which gives a good length for layering with other necklaces.  Don't miss your chance to be a true gunslinger with this piece!!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Faucet Bracelet
description: Monserat de Lucca designs this interesting and unique bracelet.  One of the best things about this piece is that it's square..something not seen frequently and also provides a cool contrast to one's wrist.  It is made of 100% brass and measures 2.4 inches by 2.4 inches.  Another cool aspect..the faucet actually turns!  This bracelet looks great layered (see image) and can be nicely paired with other metals!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Guitar Case Necklace
description: For the guitar lover in us all!!  This 100% brass necklace comes from Monserat De Lucca.  It's a really fun piece that is sure to draw compliments!  The chain measures in at 14 inches.  The guitar case is approximately 2.5 inches wide and 1 inch at it's highest point.  The coolest aspect..the case actually opens up and it's definitely possible to store something in there!!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Zebra Necklace
description: This necklace is handmade in Dallas by F. is for Frank.  This piece is super cool and exciting!  It's a cast pewter zebra head pendant with an antique satin finish.  The zebra measures at 1.5 inches tall and at it's widest point is approximately .75 inches.  The chain is sterling silver and is 10 inches long making it a great layering piece.  The detail in the zebra head is amazing and sure to grab attention!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Stitched Arrow Necklace
description: This necklace from Kris Nations is made in Half Moon Bay, CA.  The arrow is a symbol of protection and a beautiful muse for jewelry.  This arrow pendant is cut from recycled brass and plated in 14k gold.  The tail end of the arrow has a stitched linen (available at Custard in two colors). The arrow measures at 2.75 inches wide and .5 inch tall at it's tallest point.  The chain consists of the same metals and is 16 inches long.  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Bixby Big Bangle
description: This beautiful bangle can be worn by itself of layered perfectly with other bracelets!  It is from Adesso and handmade in Santa Barbara, CA.  This bangle is made of hand-forged brass with silk thread which Custard has five different colors!  The bangle measures in at a diameter of 2.5 inches and has a wonderful heavy look without the real heavy weight!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Western Bracelet
description: This is one of the most unique items at Custard!  The western bracelet is from Monserat de Lucca and is made of 100% brass.  The piece has a 6 inch circumference but is adjustable larger or smaller.  The detail in this bracelet is amazing.  First off, there is a gun and holster and the gun can be in or out of the holster!  The gun is connected with a 2 inch chain.  The revolver measures in at 1.5 inches wide and 1 inch at its tallest point.  The buckle is 1 inch wide and has some really bullet details right next to it!  This is a sure fire great piece and one not to miss!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Dreamcatcher Necklace
description:
A Custard favorite!!

Handmade brass and silver spears with brass beads on a gunmetal chain

Hangs 9.5"

Natalie Joy is an independent jewelry designers based in Portland, OR.

name: Five Point Spear Necklace
description:
Handmade brass spear beads with alternating patina on a gunmetal chain

Hangs 9"

Natalie Joy is an independent designer based in Portland, OR.

name: Rhino Skull Necklace
description: This necklace brings the safari to you!  It's a brass piece from Monserat De Lucca that is very interesting.  The rhino skull is richly detailed and measures in at 1.5 inches wide and 1 inch at it's tallest.  The chain is beaded brass and it's length is 14 inches.  This is a very original piece that is waiting for someone like you!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Dress Form Necklace
description: A must for any fashion designer or fan of clothing!!  The dress form necklace is done with wonderful craftsmanship from Monserat de Lucca.  It's 100% brass and spectacular.  The pendant measures in at approximately 3 inches tall and at it's widest point is right at an inch.  The chain is 14.5 inches long.  This is a great piece and sure to stand out in your jewelry collection!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: T. Rex Skeleton Necklace
description: This is truly a fun piece!  The t.rex necklace comes from Monserat De Lucca and is made of 100% brass and it is 3D!!  The detail on this piece is exceptional!  The chain length is 28 inches which makes it a great layering necklace.  The t.rex is 3.5 inches at it's tallest point and 2.5 inches at it's widest.  You are sure to get a lot of compliments on this necklace so don't miss your chance own one!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Triceratops Skull Necklace
description: Are you a dinosaur fanatic?? I know you are!  Here is the perfect necklace.  It's a brass triceratops skull Monserat De Lucca.  The chain is 14 inches long.  The skull pendant is 1.25 inches at its widest point and is approximately 1.75 inches high.  The pendant will lay about 1 inch off the chest when worn.  This is a really cool piece that can easily be layered  and will make a perfect gift!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Desert Sky Earrings
description: What can be better than handmade jewelry from Franklin, TN?? Not much. These earrings are from Modern Bronze and they are stunning!!  Main material used in the earring is of course bronze.  The stone is turquoise and the ear wires are gold fill.  These earrings will hang approximately 3 inches and the diameter of the circle is 1 inch.

name: "rings are true friends" and "no star" ox silver rings
description: Handmade in USA, oxidized sterling silver rings with two different, sweet inscriptions on them.  The plain oxidized  bands are engraved with: "no star to me as bright as thee" and "rings and true friends are without ends" By workhorse

name: Agata Necklace
description:
This leather necklace from ADA makes a great statement! Round leather cord is accented with handmade jump rings. 

18" long

name: Evolution Skull Knuckle Ring
description: This two finger ring comes from Monserat de Lucca and consists of three skulls side-by-side depicting an evolution pattern.  Really cool and really one-of-a-kind!  The ring is brass and is easily adjustable to size because of the hoops not being fully closed.  The ring measures in at 1.75 inches across the fingers and rises approximately a .5 inch off the finger.  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Mad Men Necklace
description: This item is a Custard favorite!  The mad men necklace is handmade in Dallas by F. is for Frank.  The pendant is very interesting!  It depicts a man seemingly walking to the edge and jumping.  The pendant is made of cast pewter with an antique satin finish.  It's 1.75 inches wide and and it's tallest point is approximately 1 inch.  The chain is sterling silver and is 10 inches.  A truly unique piece that is waiting for that truly unique owner!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Rising Bracelet
description: Another gorgeous design from Sharon Kaplan!!  This piece is handmade in California and is fire-enameled copper.  The design is a true ID bracelet design and sits wonderfully atop the wrist!  The pendant is 2 inches long and .5 inches wide.  The chain is also copper and is adjustable up to 2 inches.  True one-of-a-kind and one not to be overlooked!!

name: Tryst Triangle Earrings
description: Make a statement with these earring from Sharon Kaplan out of Los Angeles!  These triangles are made of fire-enameled copper and are completely handmade by the artist.  The chain are ear wire are also copper.  The triangles 1 inch at their tallest and approximately .75 inches at their widest.  These earrings will hang from the ear approximately 3 inches.

name: Gap Hoops
description: These angular hoops are beautiful accompaniments for all seasons!  These earrings are 1.5 inches in width and copper with 14 karat gold-fill earwires.  They are light and pristine! The gap hoops are produced by Lila Rice who makes all her jewelry in Brooklyn, NY.

name: Pamela Pendant Necklace
description: This beautiful piece of jewelry is handmade by Sharon Kaplan in LA.  It's a fire-enameled copper pendant on a 9 inch copper chain.  This piece is a true original and is so colorful and detailed!!  The pendant itself is 1.5 inches in diameter.

name: Turquoise Deerskin Wrap Bracelet
description:
Handmade by two sisters in Franklin, TN, this unique wrap bracelet features deerskin leather and chunks of beautiful turquoise secured with hand hammered bronze. A labor of love, this piece has a tie closure. 

Measures approximately 30"

name: Pyrite Goddess Earrings
description:
These shapely earrings are handcrafted in Franklin, TN by two sisters out of bronze and feature individually hand-wired pyrite stones. 

2.75" from the top of the ear wire to base

name: Kacy Clutch
description: These envelope clutches are produced in California by ADA.  They are made of cowhide leather that is from a family farm in Argentina.  The dimensions of the bag are 9.5 inches by 5.5 inches.  The inside pocket measures in at 4 inches by 3 inches.  The clasp is magnetic with silver hardware.  Custard has two different styles and three different colors.  These clutches are immaculate and built to last! Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: African Record Bead necklace
description: Handmade in USA, these fair trade African record bead necklaces spice up any outfit.  Worn together these make a bright statement, but they are long enough to layer with other pieces in your jewelry box, and are detailed enough to be worn alone.  Available in four colours, black, orange, yellow, and green, each piece is made by hand and unique.  The chain is brass, and each necklace has unique brass beads on each end of the stacked record beads.   By: Dream Collective

name: Large disk hoops
description: Handmade by Lila Rice, these large disk hoops are strong and beautiful.  Available in brass and copper, these earrings will make a statement, but can be worn every day.  As a favorite designer in Custard Boutique, Lila Rice, holds a special place in our hearts for her amazing attention to details and texture she brings to each piece.  These earrings will change colour with your natural body chemistry and only get more beautiful with age and time.  Brass is on the left, and copper is on the right in the joint photo, they are next to a quarter for size.

name: Rhiannon
description: If you or someone you know is a horse lover then this ring is for you!!  This beautiful piece from Workhorse is an oxidized sterling silver double horse head ring.  The horse head measure in at approximately .5 inches and sit on top of the finger remarkably well.  This ring is handmade in Los Angeles and comes in size 6.5.  The incredible details in this ring give it a so much charm!!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Mountain Hoops
description: These gorgeous earrings are from Lila Rice and are handmade in New York City!  At their widest, these earrings are 2 inches across.  The metal is a brushed brass with 14 karat gold-fill earwires.  For a Lila Rice piece, the mountain hoops are also very lightweight!  These earrings will make an amazing gift for that special someone!!

name: Arrow Hoops
description: A true statement piece!!  The arrow hoops are hammered, brushed  antiqued brass by Lila Rice.  Handmade in Brooklyn, these earrings are 3 inches long and 2 inches at their widest point and have 14 karat gold-fill earwires.  The arrow hoops are actually the personal favorite of the designer and are sure to be yours as well!!

name: Bunny Cuff Gold Brass
description:
Bunny ears and bunny feet, something so cute and so very sweet! 

This cuff by boyNYC is so cute, it will melt whoever lays eyes on it. 

Handcrafted of brass in Brooklyn

name: Sun Hoops
description: Edgy, sophisticated, and just plain gorgeous!  These are great terms to define the sun hoops from Lila Rice.  These beauties are 3 inches long with amazing sun ray detail along the outside edge.  The sun hoops are handmade in Brooklyn and are bright brass with 14 karat gold-fill earwires.  Inspiration for this item is said to have come from Dia de los Muertos face-painting.  These are a real head-turner and ones not to miss!!

name: La Mer Interchangeable Gift Boxes
description: Here is one of Custards most popular items in a gift box set!!  The La Mer wrap watches have been a staple at Custard since day one.  Here their signature square watch face (comes in gold and silver) is interchangeable amongst three washed Italian leather straps!  Each watch strap is 16 inches long and 5/8 inch wide.  These watches are handmade in the United States, with Japanese movement, mineral crystal, and a shower proof case!  There is a 2 year warranty from La Mer with these watches, if ever a problem. Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

options.name: Washed gray, teal, and royal blue straps with gold face
Camel, black, and washed gray straps with silver face

name: Man Vs. Animal Cuff
description: Man versus animal...who wins??  You do with this awesome cuff!!  We have two options for you on this piece.  We have it available in either oxidized brass or a sterling silver plate.  These pieces are made in Brooklyn by boyNYC.  Both the skulls on this cuff are approximately .5 X .5 inches.

name: Four Human Skull Bracelet
description: A very bold piece by Monserat de Lucca that has four brass, human skulls lined on a bracelet.  If you have an eerie side to you this bracelet might be right up your alley!  The bracelet measures in at 9 inches long and each skull is .75 inches by 1 inch.  The bar clasp is etched with "come from paradise" and "defy".  This is another great layering piece and goes well with all metals.  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Triangle Disc Hoops
description: These beauties are handmade in Brooklyn, NY by Lila Rice.  These hoops are 2 inches across and have a triangular cut-out.  The metal is a bright brass which really gleams in the sun!  The clasps are a 14 karat gold-fill earwire.  These earrings are sure to make you stand out at any event!!

name: Open Triangle Disc Hoops
description: Lila Rice is a marvel of jewelry craftsmanship!  These inspiring earrings are hammered bright brass with 14 karat gold-fill earwires.  This piece is handmade by the designer in Brooklyn.  The hoops are 2 inches across with angular cut outs.  These earrings are a cool twist on another Lila Rice piece, the Triangle Disc Hoops.  This item is a great accent to any outfit, from an elegant cocktail dress to a tee with denim!

name: Minna
description: This simple little piece from Workhorse is perfect for layering with other necklaces!  The Minna is a 16 inch oxidized sterling silver chain with an oxidized sterling silver shield pendant.  The shield measures at 5/8 of an inch and has an 1.5 pt white diamond in the center.  The piece is the ultimate in simplicity and elegance! Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Large Gap Hoops
description: Simply put, these are the bigger version of Lila Rice's gap hoops.  These earrings are 3 inches across and Custard has them in antiqued brass and copper with 14 karat gold-fill earwires.  Each hoop is handmade in New York by the designer and is one of the most elegant pieces at Custard!

name: Gem Hoops
description: One of the more unique pieces from Lila Rice.  The gem hoops are intricately cut and textured and are really easy to wear.  Each of the gem hoops are hand-printed with mesh so that each piece varies and has its own personality!  The earrings are 2.5 inches long and 1.5 inches at its widest. They are made of antiqued brass with 14 karat gold-fill earwires.

name: Chief Pendant
description:
Dream Collective brings another great hand enameled piece. Tribal inspired, this piece is a handmade labor of love. 

Brass and multi-color enamel pendant on chain with snake clasp. 2 inches long and .75 inches across.

name: Catalina Clutch
description: This fold-over envelope clutch is from ADA and is handmade of genuine Argentine leather.  It has an angled external zipper closure and also an internal zipper with card holders.  It measures at 11.5 inches by 4.5 inches and when unfolded it's 9 inches tall.  Custard has two color options and they are exquisite!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Dream Catcher Pendant
description:
2.25 inches tall and .75 inches across, this hand enameled dream catcher is with you every step of the way. Detailed down to the snake closure, this necklace from Dream Collective is a great example of their back to basics nature. 

Made from oxidized brass, on a 30 inch chain.

name: Nerd Bird Cuff
description:
Nerd Bird is a unique conversation piece, to say the least. This brass cuff was handmade in Brooklyn, created by designer boyNYC. From his feet to his glasses, this bypass cuff layers well with other pieces including our La Mer wrap watches. 

His head is 1 1/2 long, and 1/2 inch wide
His Feet are approximately 3/4 inch wide, and 1 inch long

name: Cupid
description: The Cupid necklace from Workhorse is so cool!  The pendant is an oxidized sterling silver closed hand holding onto an oxidized sterling silver arrow.  The arrow is approximately 1 inch and slides back and forth within the hand as well which is amazing!  The chain is 18 inches and is also oxidized sterling silver.  Don't miss your chance to own this one-of-a-kind piece!!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Estelle
description: The cuff is amazing! It's an oxidized sterling silver bypass cuff with two six-point stars.  In the middle of each star is a diamond..one black and one white!  The Estelle is handmade in Los Angles and it's from Workhorse. Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Pyramid Hoops
description: Lightweight, seductive, and made in the USA...our favorite concepts!  The pyramid hoops are from Lila Rice and are handmade in New York City.  These earring are a bright brass, 3 inches long, and have 14 karat gold-fill earwires.  This piece is a a favorite of all Custard employees and looks great on every woman!

name: Sobresita Clutch
description: This clutch is made of Argentine leather and is from ADA.  It is a great accompaniment to any night-out attire!  It has a fold-over front, external zipper pocket, removable chain strap, interior pockets and card holders.  It measures at 10 inches by 6 inches and when unfolded is 9 inches tall.  The strap is 34 inches in length and hangs down 17 inches when on the shoulder.  This bag has a beautiful metallic silver color which is sure to bring attention from jealous passersby!  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Chevron Cuff
description: Like primitive relics, Dream Collective sends us back to a simpler time with these hand enameled brass cuffs. Two colors to choose from. Approximately 1/4 of an inch tall.

name: Arrow Necklace
description: This is a beautiful pullover necklace from Lila Rice.  The arrow pendant is 3 inches long and is hammered brass.  Their is a little extra detail thrown in on the arrow with a hand-forged sterling silver rivet.  The chain is 28 inches and is an oxidized brass curb chain.  A remarkable necklace that is completely deserving of a good home!

name: Man Vs. Animal 3D Cuff
description: If you want something that's really cool, here it is!! The 3d man vs. animal bracelet comes in either rose gold or gold plate over brass.  They are handmade in Brooklyn by boyNYC.  The man skull is approximately .75 X .75 inches.  The animal skull is 1.5 inch by .5 inches.  Don't miss your chance on this original!

name: Swan Cuff
description:
Swan are elegant, beautiful yet feisty creatures.  We love the juxtaposition of these amazing birds.  In greek mythology it is said that upon death that swan can sing beautifully, an ultimate transformation of voice.  This is where the saying swan song comes from.  

 

One size fits most. The cuffs are malleable and can be shaped to your wrist. 


 All pieces handmade in Los Angeles. Made of 100% reclaimed metal.  Available in a gold patina.

 

1.25 inches in height by 2.25 inches in diameter

name: Shark Tooth Cuff
description:
Sharks are an integral part of the oceans eco system.  The play a role of predator that helps to keep things delicately balanced.  They are also warriors of the sea. If you need some warrior energy in your life this is the cuff for you!


All pieces are handmade in Los Angeles. Forged from 100% reclaimed metal.


One size fits most.  The cuffs are malleable, and can be formed to your wrist.

3 inches tall, by 2.25 inches in diameter.  

Available in a gold patina.

name: Armor Necklace
description: The armor necklace...it's just majestic!  Handmade by Lila Rice in New York, this piece consists of a 4 inch textured, antiqued brass pendant on a 30 inch chain.  The chain is cool because it can be worn crossed at the chest or straight.  We also carry a slightly smaller pendant that has a checkerboard pattern.  Both necklaces are pullovers and are truly stunning!

name: Orthia
description: The design of this cuff was taken from an antique albert chain and its T-bar.  This piece from Workhorse is oxidized sterling silver for the band and 14 karat gold for the spike.  The spike is approximately 1 inch in length.  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Gillian Julius Black Cuff
description: Mixed metals adds so much dimension to your jewelry. This hand made in the USA cuff is made from one continuous piece of wax coated black thread. The gold and silver tubes are also hand made by the designer. This bracelet comes in one size. It would be a great addition to your jewelry box!

name: Gillian Julius Gold and Silver Cuff
description: Don't miss out on this mixed metals Gillian Julius cuff! The continuous piece of wax coated thread, along with the hand made gold and silver tubes, makes this cuff one of a kind. Completely hand made by the designer in Los Angeles, California, the cuff is 2 1/2" wide and adds sparkle to any outfit. Each bracelet is one size.

name: Gillian Julius Brass Cuff
description: One continuous piece of hunter green wax coated thread makes up the base of this gorgeous hand made cuff. Adorned with brass tubes, this 2 1/2" bracelet really stands out. This cuff comes in one size. It is made in Los Angeles, California by the designer herself. A great addition to any jewelry collection, get yours today!

name: Shania
description: This is a beautiful pair of broken arrow stack rings by Workhorse from Los Angeles.  They are mixed sterling silver and 14 karat gold with white pave diamonds.  They can be worn as a pair or separated and look elegant either way!  This is one of Workhorse's most popular designs and a favorite among Custard staff.  They are sold only as a pair and come in size 7.  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Studded Wallet
description: This is a handcrafted Italian leather wallet made in California. This amazing studded wallet will be enough to carry alone, but dynamic coming out of a handbag.  15 rows of 6 hand placed studs grace the front of this fantastic piece, along with a handle on the back, boasting 9 studs.  The back of the wallet has a zipper compartment and the top of the wallet has zipper entry.  Inside you will find a clear area for your ID, and 2 pockets, as well as 4 large slots for cards.  Made by Calleen Cordero.

name: Zena Clutch with Serpentine Studs
description: This Calleen Cordero piece is handmade in Hollywood using fine, Italian leather!  The front and carrying strap are embedded with gold and silver studs in a serpent pattern.  Inside the clutch are 6 card slots and 3 sleeves for storage.  Also, there is zippered storage compartment on the back!  This item has magnetic clasps for easy open and sturdy closing.  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Zena Clutch
description: Just an amazing clutch!!  Produced in Hollywood, CA by Calleen Cordero, this clutch adds a distinct air of sophistication to any outfit.  There are 11 rows of stud work on the front of this piece as well as studs on the carrying strap.  This item is crafted from the finest Italian leather and features magnetic clasps for opening and closing.  Inside there are 6 card slots and 3 pockets for storage.  The back of the clutch also has a zippered storage compartment.  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Mila Wallet/Clutch with Daisy Studs
description: The most subtle of the mila wallets from Calleen Cordero, this item is simply beautiful!  This piece is handmade in Hollywood and uses only the best Italian leather which has been studded on the front and the back strap.  Inside there are 5 card slots, a translucent i.d. holder, and two compartment for loose money.  Also, on the back, the is a  zippered pocket for extra storage.  Tracking and insurance is included in the shipping price.

name: Mila Wallet/Clutch with Raised Studs
description: This is a bold, elegant clutch perfect for an evening out in the city!  This wallet is made from Italian leather in Hollywood, CA.  There are three color options with this piece, making it easy to coordinate with your ensemble.  There a 5 card slots and a drivers license holder.  Also, there are two inside and one outside zippered compartments for money, etc.  The wallet is 8.5 inches long and 4 inches wide.  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.

name: Mila Wallet/Clutch
description: This wallet is most assuredly a statement piece!  It is handmade in Hollywood, CA from the finest Italian leather by Calleen Cordero.  The studs on the front are serpentine as well as the strap on the back.  The inside boasts ample room for loose money and has 5 slots for your credit cards.  There is also a clear slot for an i.d.   There is also a zippered storage compartment on the back of the wallet.  Tracking and insurance are included in the shipping price.
